A mascot is a symbol, character, animal, or figure that represents a company, organization, team, product, or brand. 
It helps people recognize and remember that organization.

Simple Definition

Mascot = A symbolic character that represents a brand or organization.

| Company / Organization | Mascot           | Meaning                                |
| ---------------------- | ---------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| PostgreSQL             | 🐘 Elephant      | Strength, reliability, memory          |
| Linux                  | 🐧 Tux (Penguin) | Friendly, open-source operating system |
| Android                | 🤖 Android Robot | Android mobile platform                |
| Mozilla Firefox        | 🦊 Fox           | Firefox web browser                    |
| GitHub                 | 🐱 Octocat       | GitHub platform                        |


